18:46.887 --> 18:48.419
- Whoo!
- [sighs]

18:48.421 --> 18:50.555
- [cheers and applause]
- Yeah, baby!

18:50.557 --> 18:52.090
[cheers and applause]

18:52.092 --> 18:54.159
Is my face okay?

18:56.096 --> 18:58.496
Oh, this was real.

19:00.133 --> 19:02.901
Did your zipper
hold up today?

19:02.903 --> 19:04.936
It didn't, thank you.

19:04.938 --> 19:07.572
I'm currently stuck
in these pants.

19:07.574 --> 19:09.073
Well, you could
let me help you.

19:09.075 --> 19:10.642
I don't want you
to ever touch me again.

19:10.644 --> 19:12.610
I'm sorry for
making you feel bad.

19:12.612 --> 19:15.446
I figured it was a no-strings
thing for you too.

19:15.448 --> 19:16.714
I don't do
one-night stands.

19:16.716 --> 19:18.116
Two, three, maybe four,

19:18.118 --> 19:19.918
depending on what I still
need to accomplish.

19:19.920 --> 19:21.486
You mean there was stuff
we didn't do?

19:21.488 --> 19:24.489
A lot of stuff.
Sex isn't casual to me.

19:24.491 --> 19:26.891
I want the woman that
I'm with to feel amazing.

19:26.893 --> 19:28.493
And I did!

19:28.495 --> 19:30.762
Rodrigo, this may not sound
romantic,

19:30.764 --> 19:34.966
but last night felt amazing
to me because it was so casual.

19:34.968 --> 19:37.068
All I do is stress
about work or the kids,

19:37.070 --> 19:39.137
and it was nice
for just one evening

19:39.139 --> 19:40.838
not to think
about any of that,

19:40.840 --> 19:44.175
to just think about
myself for a change.

19:44.177 --> 19:45.510
I did that for you?

19:45.512 --> 19:48.980
Oh, you made me feel
very special.

19:48.982 --> 19:51.983
I guess this means
Ana's open-book mantra

19:51.985 --> 19:54.752
had some merit, not that
she needs to hear that.

19:54.754 --> 19:56.087
That can be our new secret,

19:56.089 --> 19:58.790
since everyone knows
about our old one.

19:58.792 --> 20:01.826
Well, they don't know
we spent another night together.

20:01.828 --> 20:04.162
Oh. [giggles] Did we?

20:04.164 --> 20:07.832
I guess I need help
getting out of these pants.

20:07.834 --> 20:09.367
Oh, then I'll go get
my scissors.

20:09.369 --> 20:10.802
Oh, oh, okay.

20:10.804 --> 20:12.237
I'm gonna go work
on my flirting.

20:12.739 --> 20:15.406
Oh, I'm so happy
we're gonna be friends now!

20:15.408 --> 20:17.374
No, we're not friends.

20:17.376 --> 20:19.009
But as a reward for
your loyalty.

20:19.011 --> 20:20.711
